aVPresident Donald Trump on Friday took to Twitter to encourage everyone in the path of Hurricane Irma to stay safe.\u000a\u000aHurricane Irma is of epic proportion, perhaps bigger than we have ever seen. Be safe and get out of its way,if possible. Federal G is ready! \u2014 Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) September 8, 2017\u000a\u000aIrma is currently a Category 4 hurricane barreling down on Florida, where it's expected to start raking the Florida Keys early Sunday.\u000a\u000aTrump also gave a shoutout to the Coast Guard for its work in the aftermath of Hurricane Harvey last week.
